{{Quote|We'll have to pick you up a toothbrush to clean that stench out of your choppers.|Mission Vao to Zaalbar|<ref name="kotor">''[[Star Wars: Knights of the Old Republic]]''</ref>}}
A '''toothbrush''' was an instrument used to clean [[Tooth/Legends|teeth]].

Among its many uses, a [[groomer]] could be used as a toothbrush.<ref name="Holiday Special">''[[The Star Wars Holiday Special]]''</ref>

